title: Go Back to Stashed Changes in Git
tags: _method git @zettel
roam-id: b506e978-5737-4ed7-bc6e-e4b8836ad6e7
type: text/markdown

``` shell
git stash list # to get the target stash
git stash apply stash@{N} # replace N with your stash id
```

if everything is okay and your stashed changes are applied then you can safely delete your stash
